abstract: The U.S. Environmental Protection Agency and the Justice Department said a federal appeals court should reverse a lower court verdict finding Bayer AG liable in the case of a California man who blamed its Roundup weed killer for his cancer.

lead_paragraph: (Reuters) - The U.S. Environmental Protection Agency and the Justice Department said a federal appeals court should reverse a lower court verdict finding Bayer AG liable in the case of a California man who blamed its Roundup weed killer for his cancer.
headline_main: U.S. Government Says Verdict in Bayer's Roundup Case Should Be Reversed
headline_print_headline: U.S. Government Says Verdict in Bayer's Roundup Case Should Be Reversed
